Introducing Money Maker, a fun clicker game extension for your Chrome browser! Start with just a click and watch your earnings grow as you unlock powerful upgrades and exciting casino games.

Features:

Simple clicker gameplay: Just click the "Earn Money!" button to start earning money right away.
Upgrades: Purchase upgrades to increase your earnings per click and multiply your wealth.
Casino games: Take a break from clicking and test your luck at casino games for a chance to win big.
Save progress: Your game progress is saved automatically in local storage, so you can pick up right where you left off.
Help and Credits: Learn how to play and get support when you need it.
